abstract: St Louis Rams defeat Tampa Bay Buccaneers, 31-23, in what may be team's last game in city as owners continue bid to move to Los Angeles.
lead_paragraph: The Rams’ 31st-ranked offense had a big game in what might have been the franchise’s last game in St. Louis.

headline.main: Rams, Facing Possible Move, Win at Home
